reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for travel and daily use!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Amazon Basics 4 Piece Packing Travel Organizer Cubes Set in the medium size, and I can confidently say that these cubes have transformed the way I pack for travel. They are an absolute game-changer!First and foremost, these medium-sized cubes are the perfect balance between space-saving and capacity. They fit seamlessly in my suitcase, optimizing every inch of available space. The depth of these cubes allows me to neatly pack my clothes without worrying about excessive wrinkles. It's like having a mini dresser inside my suitcase!The organization these cubes provide is exceptional. I assigned each cube a specific clothing type, making it incredibly easy to find what I need without rummaging through my entire luggage. Whether it's shirts, pants, or even accessories, these cubes keep everything neatly separated.One of the standout features is how they keep my clothes relatively wrinkle-free. The design and depth of these cubes allow me to fold my clothes the way I want, resulting in minimal wrinkles upon arrival. It's a time-saver, especially when I'm attending events where presentation matters.The quality of these cubes is top-notch. The zippers are sturdy and glide smoothly, and the fabric is durable and easy to clean. I've used them on multiple trips, and they still look and function as if they were brand new.The versatility of these cubes is another highlight. They're not just for travel; I've found countless uses for them in my daily life, from organizing my gym bag to keeping my closet tidy. These cubes are a multi-purpose solution.In summary, the Amazon Basics 4 Piece Packing Travel Organizer Cubes Set in the medium size has become an essential part of my travel routine. They make packing more efficient, keep my clothes organized, and help maintain a polished appearance. If you're looking for a game-changer in your travel packing, I highly recommend these cubes. They are versatile, well-made, and worth every penny.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These making packing so much easier!
reviews.reviewText: I always use these when traveling! They work great and hold much more than you would expect. Some items are a little wrinkled, depending on the fabric. I typically roll my clothes and then put them in the packing cube, minimizes the wrinkles. I love that my clothes are organized and make it easy to find what I need. They are like ones that Travel Fashion Girl used to sell. Her website has tricks on how to use these like a compressible packing cube.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy Packing and Good Zippers
reviews.reviewText: Never was really into packing cubes until now! Great variety of sizes for different uses. At first, I thought the material was a bit flimsy but once filled, it feels more sturdy. I would still try not to over pack these as it could rip. Still, a decent price… Here’s a list of pros/cons.Pros:-Sizes fit everything from shirt, pants, underwear, socks.- great organization- some expansion and easy glide zipper- mesh for breathability- handles for transporting in/out of suitcase- nice colorCons:- can take a bit of stretching to fit shoes. I would probably just use a bigger bag or plastic bag instead.- material is not the thickest and will likely rip or get holes over time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Packing cubes are great for organizing, these work well
reviews.reviewText: I like using packing cubes to organize clothing for travel. They make packing and unpacking easier. Living out of a suitcase or duffel bag is *much* easier with the cubes to keep things separate. I even leave smaller clothing like socks and underwear in the cubes when I have a hotel with drawers. Amazon's inexpensive packing cubes have held up well in my travels and their relatively inexpensive cost means I can buy enough to keep everything organized. My wife and I often travel together, so we each have our own color. Even when our stuff ends up mingled for packing, it is easy to separate.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These make a lot of sense for traveling
reviews.reviewText: We used these for our 6 week SE Asia trip and loved them. We moved hotels every few days and these make it so much easier to stay organized. All shirts in one bag, all underwear in another etc. Or if we knew we'd only stay for one night somewhere, we'd just put everything for the next day into one bag and all we had to take out of the big suitcase that day was that one bag. Totally useful, seem good quality. None of the two sets we got broke or was damaged. Will certainly use again.

reviews.reviewTitle: Toda maleta ya debería venir con esto
reviews.reviewText: Son excelentes para mantener tu maleta bien organizada

These packing cubes were purchased for a 10-day trip overseas. I was a bit hesitant to purchase them at first as I had another set of packing cubes that didn't have good quality. The Amazon Basics packing cubes are actually very durable and good quality for the price. It is a bit cheaper as well compared to some of the other packing cubes listed on Amazon. They aren't the kind of cubes that compress so it won't get smaller but at least keeps your clothes organized. The set of 4 are all the same size so don't expect to have a variety of different sized packing cubes.
